              {
                "type": "tableCell",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "TF-IDF + LR — inspect feature weights directly"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "blockquote",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Always run the TF-IDF + Logistic Regression baseline first. On many real-world datasets with enough data and reasonable feature engineering, it matches or outperforms fine-tuned transformers while training in seconds instead of hours. A 1% accuracy gain from BERT rarely justifies 100× the compute."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
